SCOPE OF THIS BSD-3-CLAUSE LICENSE

The BSD-3-Clause license above governs only the cloud-boot/goquake1 wrapper
code authored fresh for this repository: the bare-metal probe glue, virtio
adapters in backend/tamago/, the embedpak shareware archive loader, the
provable-test harness, the harvest-reference oracle generator, the transpile
pipeline tooling in internal/transpile/, and the CI workflows.

The transpiled Quake engine -- the Go code produced by ccgo from quakeforge
C source under engine/ -- inherits the upstream quakeforge license: GPL-2.0
or later. See engine/LICENSE.engine for the verbatim upstream notice. The
ccgo translation is a derivative work for licensing purposes; redistribution
must comply with GPL-2.0 for that subtree.

In practical terms: link against this repository's engine subtree only if
your downstream is GPL-2.0-compatible. The wrapper layer (backend, embedpak,
cmd, internal/transpile, .github) remains under BSD-3-Clause so it can be
copy-pasted into other cloud-boot projects without dragging GPL onto them.
